'''乙酸钚酰钠'''是一种钚化合物，化学式为NaPuO<sub>2</sub>(CH<sub>3</sub>COO)<sub>3</sub>，是难溶于水的粉色晶体，有放射性。

==制备==
乙酸钚酰钠可由{{link-ru|硝酸钚酰|Нитрат плутонила}}、[[硝酸钠|硝酸钠]]和[[乙酸|乙酸]]在溶液中反应得到：
:: <math>\mathsf{ PuO_2(NO_3)_2 + NaNO_3 + 3 CH_3COOH \ \xrightarrow{}\ NaPuO_2(CH_3COO)_3\downarrow + 3 HNO_3 }</math>

它也可由硝酸钚酰和饱和[[乙酸钠|乙酸钠]]溶液反应，沉淀得到。<ref name=Jones />
==性质==
它是粉色晶体，属[[立方晶系|立方晶系]]，P2<sub>1</sub>3[[空间群|空间群]]，晶胞参数a=10.670 Å，Z=4，与[[乙酸铀酰钠|NaUO<sub>2</sub>(CH<sub>3</sub>COO)<sub>3</sub>]]同构。<ref name=Jones>{{cite journal|journal=The Journal of Chemical Physics|volume=23|issue=11|language=en|issn=0021-9606|date=1955-11|pages=2105–2107|doi=10.1063/1.1740675|url=http://aip.scitation.org/doi/10.1063/1.1740675|title=Infrared Spectra and Structure of the Crystalline Sodium Acetate Complexes of U(VI), Np(VI), Pu(VI), and Am(VI). A Comparison of Metal‐Oxygen Bond Distance and Bond Force Constant in this Series|accessdate=2020-09-08|author=Llewellyn H. Jones}}</ref>

